name: GetSense
tag_list: mobile, cloud, offshore, outsourcing, scrum, agile, open-source
overview:
GetSense provides Integration & Software Development Services.

The company specializes in Java and Google App Engine Software Development and adopted Scrum Agile Methodology to deliver Software Solutions.

It’s located in Buenos Aires, Argentina and has customers in Europe and Argentina.
